Package api

Class Edge

java.lang.Object
api.Edge
All Implemented Interfaces:
edge_data
public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
implements edge_data
This class represents the set of operations applicable on a directional edge(src,dest) in a (directional) weighted graph.
